**Lower priority (optional):**
- Specialized items for specific risks
- Redundant supplies
- Rarely used items

## Kit Maintenance

**Pre-trip:**
- Check all items present
- Verify medication expiration dates
- Replace used items from last trip
- Review contents and locations

**Post-trip:**
- Restock used supplies
- Dry wet items
