## Kit Optimization Algorithms

### Weight-Utility Analysis

**Value metric:**
\`\`\`
Value = (Probability of use x Benefit if used) / Weight

High value items (carry always):
- Tourniquet: Low probability, extreme benefit, low weight
- Ibuprofen: High probability, moderate benefit, minimal weight
- Tape: Very high probability, moderate benefit, low weight

Low value items (optional):
- Rarely used specialty items
- Heavy equipment with narrow indication
- Items duplicating improvisation capability
