### Hemorrhage Control Meta-Analysis

**Tourniquet evidence synthesis:**
\`\`\`
Source: Military trauma registry, civilian mass casualty data
Sample: >10,000 tourniquet applications documented

Mortality analysis:
- Pre-shock application: Mortality 6%
- Post-shock application: Mortality 89%
- Absolute risk reduction: 83%
- NNT: 1.2 for pre-shock application

Complication rates:
- Nerve palsy: 1.5% (mostly transient)
